# Summary
This documentation page describes Amplitude Data's Google Ads integration, which imports daily ad spend, click, and impression data from Google Ads accounts, creating a "Daily Ad Metrics" event with associated properties, requiring Google Ads Customer ID and optional Manager ID for setup, with considerations around data refresh frequency and permissions.

